{"word":"G565 - ἀπέρχομαι - apérchomai - ap-erkh'-om-ahee - Come","slug":"G565","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπέρχομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>apérchomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ap-erkh'-om-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Come"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03C7;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - aperchomai</b> - <i>ap-erkh'-om-ahee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G2064\">G2064</a>; to <i>go off</i> (that is, <i>depart</i>), <i>aside</i> (that is, <i>apart</i>) or <i>behind</i> (that is, <i>follow</i>), literally or figuratively: - come, depart, go (aside, away, back, out, . . . ways), pass away, be past."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1330\">G1330</a>, <a href=\"#/G1525\">G1525</a>, <a href=\"#/G1831\">G1831</a>, <a href=\"#/G1904\">G1904</a>, <a href=\"#/G2064\">G2064</a>, <a href=\"#/G3922\">G3922</a>, <a href=\"#/G3928\">G3928</a>, <a href=\"#/G4022\">G4022</a>, <a href=\"#/G4281\">G4281</a>, <a href=\"#/G4334\">G4334</a>, <a href=\"#/G4905\">G4905</a>"}]}